features: ✅【Upgraded Magnetic-Twist-Lock Clips】Featuring a innovative 360°rotating magnetic lid that can be turned left or right with just one hand one second, made from premium ABS and PC plastic material, our cord organizer provides a secure and organized solution for cable management, firmly holds cables in place, preventing them from falling off.

✅【Acrylic Adhesive No-Residue or Damage】Enhanced acrylic adhesive pad ensures firm and long-lasting stickiness that leaves no residue or damage when removed on various surfaces like wood, glass, or ceramic tiles, making it perfect for cable management.

✅【Wide Compatibility for Most Cables】With a slot diameter of 0.3 inches (7.5mm), our magnetic cable clips can accommodate various cables including Type-C phone charger cords, HDMI cords, USB cables, lightning cords, computer power wires, laptop cords, and more.

✅【Compact and Neat Cable Management】Neatness or Mess? Say goodbye to a tangled mess of cables but for happy harvest of a clean and organized surface. For longer cables, feel free to DIY its route to any location you want. Small, compact and exquisite, the perfect cable management for you.

✅【Easy Installation Please Kindly Note】Simply clean the surface with rubbing alcohol, press the sticky pad firmly for 30 seconds, and wait one day for optimal adhesion. Your cord organizer is ready to use. Besides, several replacement adhesive pads are included in the package.
✅【Backed By Chfeila Thoughtful Service】 Chfeila support team is available 24/7 to address any concerns or issues you may have regarding our products. Your satisfaction is our top priority.
